<div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">

        <div class="govuk-notification-banner app-homepage-notifications" role="region" aria-labelledby="govuk-notification-banner-title" data-module="govuk-notification-banner">
            <div class="govuk-notification-banner__header">
                <h2 class="govuk-notification-banner__title" id="govuk-notification-banner-title">Important Notices</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="govuk-notification-banner__content">
                <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-1" data-module="govuk-details">
                    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
                        <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
                        Data publishing
                        </span>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="govuk-details__text">
                        Following successful integration of new systems, the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office (FCDO) has resumed publication to DevTracker. Data published on 28th June 2023 includes information from the period of the pause (November 2022 to May 2023). FCDO will now return to monthly publishing of data, one month in arrears. Any remaining data from the pause period will be uploaded to DevTracker in the coming months.
                    </div>
                </details>
                <details class="govuk-details" data-module="govuk-details">
                    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
                        <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
                        Security situation in Afghanistan
                        </span>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="govuk-details__text">
                        Due to the security situations in Afghanistan and Ukraine, we have temporarily removed potentially sensitive information from DevTracker to ensure the safety of partners. As programmes are reviewed and republished, information will become available on DevTracker.
                    </div>
                </details>            
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="app-card app-card-search app-card-search-no-margin">
            <img src="/assets/images/homepage-search.svg" class="app-card-search__image" alt="Search programmes">
            <div class="govuk-form-group app-card-search__input">
                <h1 class="govuk-label-wrapper">
                    <label class="govuk-label govuk-label--m" for="search">
                        Search programmes
                    </label>
                </h1>
                <div id="event-name-hint" class="govuk-hint">
                    Enter location, sector, organisation or keyword
                </div>
                <form id="searchForm" action="/search_p" class="app-search-form" method="POST"  onsubmit="return validateSearch()">
                    <p id="searchQueryError" class="govuk-error-message app-display-none">
                        <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Error:</span> Please enter a search query
                    </p>
                    <div class="app-search-form__textbox" id="searchQueryInput">
                        <input class="govuk-input query-input" id="query" name="query" type="text">
                        <button class="app-search-form__button" id="front-search-submit"
                            data-module="govuk-button"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-search-form__checkbox">
                        <div class="govuk-checkboxes govuk-checkboxes--small" data-module="govuk-checkboxes">
                            <div class="govuk-checkboxes__item">
                                <input class="govuk-checkboxes__input" id="IncludeClosedProjects"
                                    name="IncludeClosedProjects" type="checkbox" value="hmrc">
                                <label class="govuk-label govuk-checkboxes__label" for="IncludeClosedProjects">
                                    Include closed programmes
                                </label>
                                <input id="includeClosed" name="includeClosed" type="hidden" value="0">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

